## Quick Reference Checklist

### Before Production:
- [ ] maxmemory set?
- [ ] Transparent Huge Pages disabled?
- [ ] vm.overcommit_memory = 1?
- [ ] requirepass or ACL configured?
- [ ] Replication backlog configured (if using replication)?

### Before Debugging:
- [ ] Use INFO, LATENCY DOCTOR, MEMORY DOCTOR?
- [ ] Prefer SCAN over KEYS?
- [ ] Check client timeouts and retries?

